item.title: CVE-2020-2193|2024-08-04T07:01:41.151Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20echarts%20api%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins ECharts API Plugin 4.7.0-3 and earlier does not escape the parser identifier when rendering charts, resulting in a stored cross-site scripting vulnerability.

item.title: CVE-2020-2194|2024-08-04T07:01:41.090Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20echarts%20api%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins ECharts API Plugin 4.7.0-3 and earlier does not escape the display name of the builds in the trend chart, resulting in a stored cross-site scripting vulnerability.
